              <Font name="Times New Roman" size="26" style="2"/>
            </Property>
            <Property name="text" type="java.lang.String" value="A Body Mass Index (BMI) calculator is all about assessing an individual&apos;s body mass relative to their height. It&apos;s a simple tool commonly used to categorize a person&apos;s weight status, indicating whether they are underweight, normal weight, overweight, or obese. The BMI is calculated by dividing a person&apos;s weight in kilograms by the square of their height in meters. This numerical value is then interpreted using predefined categories to provide a general indication of a person&apos;s body composition and potential health risks associated with their weight. The BMI calculator serves as a quick and accessible method for individuals to monitor and evaluate their weight in relation to their height."/>
          </Properties>
        </Component>
